Maintenance:
Update a payload only as an atomic binary, manifest, and license set from a
trusted ChromeOS source. Record the source image, board, version, hashes, and
verification results here before replacing either payload.

The existing manifests retain component-package icons and platforms entries
whose referenced resources are not part of this overlay. Chromium's bundled CDM
loader ignores those unrelated fields, but they should not be removed until a
ThoriumOS runtime validation confirms that no ChromeOS packaging step consumes
them.
